== üåäCanyoning in Vercors : Les Ecouges üßó==
Lets go canyoning in Vercors! For those who don't know what canyoning is, it's basically advancing in a river usually inside a canyon by all means üòÄ This includes: jumping in water (saut), sliding (toboggans) and abseiling (descente en rappel),... So you need to know how to swim to participate! If you have never done it in the past, no biggies ! there will be a professionnal guide with us all the time making sure that we stay alive. So it will be only fun!! üòç

== ‚ùî How to participate and register? ‚ùî ==
We can be maximum 9 people (3 cars to do the activities). For now I can bring 4 people (including me) with my car. So we need another car. So, join the list (or the waiting list) and once we have the correct number I will book for the group. Cost should be between 60-65‚Ç¨ depending if we are enough or not for 4h30 of activities with Vertical Aventure.

= üí° Rules üí° ==

== ‚≠ê‚≠ê Updates ‚≠ê‚≠ê ==
> 13.07 6.30pm: event is full

=== An escape...What?? ===
For those who don't know what an escape room is: it's a game where a team (including you) is locked down during 1h maximum in a room. The objective is to go out of this room by solving enigmas and succeding as a team in small tasks. May Sherlock wits be with us! üßê

==‚ö†Ô∏è üó®Ô∏è EN/FR üó®Ô∏è‚ö†Ô∏è ==
ü¶Ö: we speak English/French in all our events and normally your level doesn't matter. However, for this specific event language is important as you should be able to read and understand French to advance and understand the game üòâ.
üêì : Nous parlons fran√ßais et anglais dans tous nos √©v√®nements et en g√©n√©ral le niveau n'a pas trop d'importance. Cependant, pour ce cas sp√©cifique, votre niveau est important car vous devez √™tre en mesure de lire et comprendre le Fran√ßais pour avancer et comprendre le jeu üòâ.

== üßê What's the plan, Watson? üßê==
The 1st step is to gather a group of 5 people. I suggest we go to this escape room: https://www.challengetheroom.fr/challenge-the-room-grenoble-notre-dame.html. When we are enough, we will all decide which enigma we do as there are several options ‚ò∫Ô∏è. I will do the booking. Tomorrow we meet next to the fountaine place Grenette and we will all go together at the escape room.

== üí° Rules üí° ==
- Don't be late, we have to respect the timing of the company üòá
- Since places are limited, please do not subscribe if you are not sure to join the event ‚ò∫Ô∏è

- Cost will be between 30 and 22‚Ç¨ depending on our number, so bring some money üí≤

- Your mask as always üò∑ (avoid contact and so on)

If you feel like it, we can share a drink, a pizza or an ice cream depending on the mood of the crowd.

== üò∑ Covid rules üò∑ ==
- Don't come if you feel sick, have fever, are contact case,...
